{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dynamic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"isEnergySavingEnabled","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/isEnergySavingEnabled","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/isenergysavingenabled"]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/isenergysavingenabled"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","title":"isEnergySavingEnabled","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"isEnergySavingEnabled"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"isEnergySavingEnabled"}],"modules":[{"name":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"}],"externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(py)isEnergySavingEnabled","symbolKind":"property"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":", if automatic energy saving should be enabled. With automatic energy saving enabled the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"base scanner view controller will, after a certain time of inactivity, enter the energy save mode by lowering the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detection\/scanning rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Version: 8.0.1","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","title":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"well as in energy saving mode."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"symbol","title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/isEnergySavingEnabled":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/isenergysavingenabled","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"isEnergySavingEnabled"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Set to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"text":", if automatic energy saving should be enabled. With automatic energy saving enabled the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"base scanner view controller will, after a certain time of inactivity, enter the energy save mode by lowering the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detection\/scanning rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"kind":"symbol","title":"isEnergySavingEnabled","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"isEnergySavingEnabled"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/isEnergySavingEnabled"}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"value":"occ","path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage","op":"replace"},{"value":"Instance Property","path":"\/metadata\/roleHeading","op":"replace"},{"value":"isEnergySavingEnabled","path":"\/metadata\/title","op":"replace"},{"value":"property","path":"\/metadata\/symbolKind","op":"replace"},{"value":[{"text":"isEnergySavingEnabled","kind":"identifier"}],"op":"replace","path":"\/metadata\/fragments"},{"value":null,"op":"add","path":"\/topicSections"},{"value":null,"op":"add","path":"\/relationshipsSections"},{"value":null,"op":"add","path":"\/seeAlsoSections"},{"value":{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"isEnergySavingEnabled"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},"op":"replace","path":"\/primaryContentSections\/0"},{"value":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/title"},{"value":[{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo